\nThe Hammer Theatreisconvenientlylocated in the heart of downtownSan Jos near an array of restaurants, hotels, and public transportation. It is a beautiful, intimate theatre featuringhigh-quality performingarts events including music, theater,\ndance, film, and more.Enjoy quality bar and concessions fare to complement the night\'s event.<u></u>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class=\"paddingLeft paddingRight margin-top-30\"][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][vc_column_text]\n<h2>Parking</h2>\nConvenient parking is available nearby at the2ndand San Carlos Garage. There\'s a $5 flat-rate after<span class=\"aBn\" tabindex=\"0\" data-term=\"goog_523603810\"><span class=\"aQJ\">6 pm</span></span>, seven nights a week and all day<span class=\"aBn\" tabindex=\"0\" data-term=\"goog_523603811\"><span class=\"aQJ\">Saturday</span></span>or<span class=\"aBn\" tabindex=\"0\" data-term=\"goog_523603812\"><span class=\"aQJ\">Sunday</span></span>(see map below). Also visit<a title=\"parksj.org link\" href=\"http://parksj.org/parking-map/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><u>San Jos\'s parking map</u></a>to see a list of otherconvenientlylocated parking garagesnear the Hammer Theatre.<u></u>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\" el_class=\"padding-left-20 padding-right-20\"][vc_column_text]\n<h2>Local Dining</h2>\nThe following restaurantsare located nearthe Hammer Theatre:\n<ul>\n 	<li><a title=\"Whispers Cafe and Creperie\" href=\"http://whisperscafe.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Whispers Cafe and Creperie</a></li>\n 	<li><a title=\"Gordon Biersch\" href=\"http://www.gordonbiersch.com/locations/san-jose?action=view\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Gordon Biersch</a></li>\n 	<li><a title=\"San Jose Bar and Grill\" href=\"http://sanjosebarandgrill.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">San Jos Bar and Grill</a></li>\n 	<li><a title=\"Mezcal\" href=\"http://mezcalrestaurantsj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Mezcal</a></li>\n</ul>\n<a title=\"San Jose Bars link\" href=\"http://www.sjsu.edu/hammertheatre/docs/restaurant-list.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><u>For a list of local restaurants, click here</u></a><a title=\"Four Points by Sheraton San Jose Downtown Yelp link\" href=\"https://www.yelp.com/biz/four-points-by-sheraton-san-jose-downtown-san-jose?osq=hotel\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">.</a><u></u>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\" el_class=\"padding-left-20\"][vc_column_text]\n<h2>Hotels</h2>\nIf you\'re looking to stay in the area, the following hotels are nearthe Hammer:\n<ul>\n 	<li><a title=\"San Jose Marriott Yelp Link\" href=\"https://www.yelp.com/biz/san-jose-marriott-san-jose?osq=hotel\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">SanJos Marriott</a></li>\n 	<li><a title=\"Fairmont San Jose Link\" href=\"https://www.yelp.com/biz/fairmont-san-jose-san-jose?osq=hotel\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Fairmont San Jos</a></li>\n 	<li><a title=\"Hyatt Place San Jose Downtown Yelp Link\" href=\"https://www.yelp.com/biz/hyatt-place-san-jose-downtown-san-jose-2?osq=hotel\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Hyatt Place San Jos Downtown</a></li>\n 	<li><a title=\"Four Points by Sheraton San Jose Downtown Yelp link\" href=\"https://www.yelp.com/biz/four-points-by-sheraton-san-jose-downtown-san-jose?osq=hotel\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Four Points by Sheraton San</a><a title=\"Four Points by Sheraton San Jose Downtown Yelp link\" href=\"https://www.yelp.com/biz/four-points-by-sheraton-san-jose-downtown-san-jose?osq=hotel\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Jos Downtown</a></li>\n</ul>\n<a title=\"San Jose Hotel Links\" href=\"https://www.yelp.com/search?find_desc=hotel&amp;l=a%3A37.335993099999996%2C-121.88377729999999%2C3141&amp;ns=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><u>To see more nearby hotels, click here</u></a><a title=\"Four Points by Sheraton San Jose Downtown Yelp link\" href=\"https://www.yelp.com/biz/four-points-by-sheraton-san-jose