1:59:52','2017-11-29 21:59:52','','ABOUT','','publish','closed','closed','','64','','','2018-06-18 12:29:03','2018-06-18 19:29:03','',0,'http://hammertheatre.staging.wpengine.com/2017/11/64/',12,'nav_menu_item','',0),(65,3,'2017-11-29 22:04:21','2017-11-29 22:04:21','[vc_row el_class=\"paddingLeft paddingRight margin-bottom-80\"][vc_column][vc_single_image image=\"403\" img_size=\"full\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class=\"paddingLeft paddingRight\"][vc_column][vc_column_text]\n<h1 class=\"margin-bottom-30\">Hammer Theatre - Partnerships, Mission, and Vision</h1>\n<ul class=\"margin-bottom-30\">\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><u>Hammer Theatre</u>: A distinctive, high-quality performance venue in the heart of downtown San Jos</span></li>\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><u>Partnership &amp; Mission</u>: Owned by the city of San Jos and operated by San Jos State University, the Hammer will serve the citys diverse communities plus the university through artistically and educationally excellent programming expressive of the unique characteristics and cultures of Silicon Valley.\n</span></li>\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><u>Vision</u>: The Hammer Theatre is a new performing arts paradigm that serves as a nexus between the broad, innovative, cultural, and educational needs of San Joss diverse community, San Jos State University and Silicon Valley by offering several performing arts series with local and global talent within an eclectic, state-of-the-art venue.\n</span></li>\n</ul>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class=\"paddingLeft paddingRight\"][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][vc_column_text]\n<h2>Programming Goal and Series Brand</h2>\n<ul class=\"margin-bottom-50\">\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><u>Programming</u>: The Hammer Theatre offers innovative programming that reflects Silicon Valleys culture of creativity, diversity, and technology so audiences can experience a broad range of live music, theatre, dance, innovative multimedia performances, National Theatre Live screenings or National Geographic Live lectures.</span></li>\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><u>Hammer Series Brands</u>: The theatre has seven distinct series brands that offer a broad range of performing arts events, live theatre films and educational lectures.\n</span></li>\n</ul>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\" el_class=\"padding-left-20\"][vc_column_text]\n<h2>Community Interest + Educational Events</h2>\n<ul class=\"margin-bottom-50\">\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><u>Hammer Community Events</u>: Performances that appeal to the San Jos community such as Asian Youth Orchestra, ElevenPlay, and San Jos Nutcracker</span></li>\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><u>Hammer Educational Events</u>: Events for the community that can educate such as National Geographic Live\n</span></li>\n</ul>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\" el_class=\"padding-left-20\"][vc_column_text]\n<h2>Academic Events</h2>\n<ul class=\"margin-bottom-50\">\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><u>Hammer + SJSU Partnership</u>: In its partnership with SJSU, the Hammer Theatre also offers workshops, master classes, and other special events that provide an educational component for its students</span></li>\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><u>Workshops &amp; Masterclasses</u>Grammy-award winning Cuarteto Latinoamericano performs at the Hammer Theatre plus offers a Masterclass for SJSU music students.</span></li>\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><u>Other Special Events</u>Sundance Film Institute, National Geographic Live\n</span></li>\n</ul>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][