oncerts are occasions fit for royaltyjazz or otherwise.</span>','Jane Monheit - San Jose Jazz Summer Fest 2018','Just out of her teens when first introduced to the jazz world, warm-toned vocalist Jane Monheit can toggle between that early innocence and a time-crafted maturity. Those qualities alone make her an ideal artist to explore some of Ella Fitzgeralds lesser-known repertoire at 2018 Summer Fest.','publish','closed','closed','','jane-monheit','','','2018-06-19 14:40:05','2018-06-19 21:40:05','',0,'http://hammertheatre.staging.wpengine.com/?post_type=tribe_events&#038;p=819',0,'tribe_events','',0),(820,11,'2018-06-19 13:00:48','2018-06-19 20:00:48','[vc_row el_class=\"margin-bottom-60\"][vc_column][vc_single_image image=\"781\" img_size=\"full\" alignment=\"center\" el_class=\"banner-img2\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_single_image image=\"780\" img_size=\"full\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class=\"vc_row wpb_row vc_row-fluid paddingLeft paddingRight\" css=\".vc_custom_1528406652221{margin-top: 3% !important;margin-bottom: 3% !important;}\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"785\" img_size=\"large\" css=\".vc_custom_1528406567778{margin-right: 3% !important;}\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h1><strong>Summer 2018 Shakespeare Series Promotion</strong></h1>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3>Buy a ticket to all three summer Shakespeare screenings</h3>\r\n<h3>for 50% off full ticket price!</h3>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_btn title=\"Buy Series\" style=\"flat\" shape=\"square\" color=\"mulled-wine\" align=\"left\" link=\"url:https%3A%2F%2Fweb.ovationtix.com%2Ftrs%2Fstore%2F34750%2Fpackages||target:%20_blank|\" css=\".vc_custom_1528744966621{margin-top: 5% !important;}\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class=\"vc_row wpb_row vc_row-fluid paddingLeft paddingRight\"][vc_column][vc_separator color=\"black\" border_width=\"2\" css=\".vc_custom_1528744777039{margin-bottom: 5px !important;}\"][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_152840